    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Beyond Karate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235030/extras/447f69873a7c561822d9806e9ffe3033.poster.avif?t=1747693192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235030/extras/447f69873a7c561822d9806e9ffe3033.webm?t=1747693192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235030/extras/447f69873a7c561822d9806e9ffe3033.mp4?t=1747693192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You know a thing or two about karate, but fighting in the streets is different. You will need to master skills inspired by a number of other martial arts including boxing, kung fu, wrestling and muay thai. Karate Punk features over 200 skills for you to mix-and-match to become the ultimate street warrior.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat about Timing and Positioning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235030/extras/f42537b0168cbc7cd52322b3d4c8e65b.poster.avif?t=1747693192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235030/extras/f42537b0168cbc7cd52322b3d4c8e65b.webm?t=1747693192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235030/extras/f42537b0168cbc7cd52322b3d4c8e65b.mp4?t=1747693192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by old-school martial arts movies of the 80s and 90s, Karate Punk pits you against hordes of enemies. You will need to master movement and timing to overcome the odds. Strike, grapple, block and parry! You may get surrounded, but you're never helpless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Setting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're Sonny, a high school student as well as a karate practitioner. One day, while you're in class, ninjas break into the classroom and kidnap your girlfriend. Now, it's up to you to save her.</p>",
